00:09:47.683 --> 00:09:49.937
was a reason to disqualify me from running.
[AI] 这是取消我参赛资格的原因。

208
00:09:49.961 --> 00:09:52.723
And believe me. people tried to tell me I shouldn't run.
[AI] 相信我。人们试图告诉我我不应该跑。

209
00:09:52.747 --> 00:09:54.604
Friends told me not to run.
[AI] 朋友告诉我不要跑。

