00:09:56.719 --> 00:09:59.600
"USA Today" mentioned maybe I shouldn't run.
[AI] 《今日美国》提到也许我不应该跑步。

212
00:09:59.624 --> 00:10:00.846
(Laughter)
[AI] （众笑）

213
00:10:00.870 --> 00:10:02.157
But no matter who it was.
[AI] 但不管是谁。

214
00:10:02.181 --> 00:10:06.924
I understood that finances are often a reason we don't let ourselves dream.
[AI] 我明白，财务状况往往是我们不让自己做梦的原因。

215
00:10:07.579 --> 00:10:10.390
I can't say that you will always overcome those obstacles.
[AI] 我不能说你总能克服这些障碍。

216
00:10:10.414 --> 00:10:13.514
